{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3a26abfc2c","title":"读《注释唐诗三百首》批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"58481d6fc8","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"3a26abfc2c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《琵琶行》：“座中拉下谁最多，江州司马青衫湿。又：“同是天涯沧落人，相逢何必曾相识。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e45394003d","type":"title","text":"读《注释唐诗三百首》批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"3a26abfc2c"},{"id":"58481d6fc8","type":"subtitle","text":"读《注释唐诗三百首》批语琵琶行并序白居易","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"3a26abfc2c"},{"id":"643230dc69","type":"paragraph","text":"江州司马，","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"3a26abfc2c"},{"id":"cdfc87d1c5","type":"paragraph","text":"元和十年，余左迁九江郡司马。明年秋，送青衫泪湿，同在客滋浦口，闻舟中夜弹琶者。听其音，锋锋然天涯。作者与有京都声。问其人，本长安倡女，尝学昆爸于琵琶演奏者有平穆、曹二善才。年长色衰，委身为费人妇。遂命等心情。白诗高酒，使快弹数曲，曲要啊然。自叙少小时欢乐处在此，不在他事，今漂沧慎悍，转徒于江湖间。余出官二年，处。其然包其然活然自安，感斯人言，是夕始觉有迁滴意，因为","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"3a26abfc2c"},{"id":"ce2d62edea","type":"subtitle","text":"平？","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"3a26abfc2c"},{"id":"62353e7409","type":"paragraph","text":"长句，歌以赠之。凡六百一十六言，命日《琵楚","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"3a26abfc2c"},{"id":"8966604005","type":"paragraph","text":"行》。[卷二七言古诗第15~16页]","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"3a26abfc2c"}],"page":{"id":"dbfe00bee5","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"3a26abfc2c","start":234,"end":234}}}},"__N_SSG":true}